  "body": "# Beehaviour\n\nThe crafting system is a core part of Minecraft, but sometimes it lacks some of the most basic recipes. Introducing these missing recipes enables more compact storage, material reusability, and craft certain items that shouldn't be that difficult to get.\n\n## Recipes\n\n### Index\n\n- [General](#general)\n- [Revert recipes](#revert-recipes)\n- [Amethyst](#amethyst)\n- [Dirts](#dirts)\n- [Equipment](#equipment)\n- [Mushrooms](#mushrooms)\n\n### General\n\n| Recipe          | Preview                                                                                                                   |\n| --------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Bamboo mosaic   | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/c7b2386e79b80ebc621ac7fbc7359d7498151898.png\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| Bone            | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/35ff9400b0a6780c397839eef2548b3bcc741351.png\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| Calcite         | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/7b2840754565d887d2964deb9daa9372e6ddaca7.png\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| Crying obsidian | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/e0f38552bceacda1cc057e568a89b5c8e0fa8322.png\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| Dead bush       | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/8a0d97fc34bba2a5728dd28f7d4753f12da823b9.gif\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| Green dye       | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/07da1c6e06567b10af0eda6c7562c3c4b0780a5c_350.webp\" width=\"200\" /> |\n| Name tag        | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/749f36ff45acf8dc207746a943673b94751ee860.png\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| Jukebox         | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/ed606ebbd0eb886ea80dedff745da938872976a8.png\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| Slabs           | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/af4e3a917bcfafc35802d1fd21b61e69f02a3eee.gif\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| String          | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/4601c16c2388013905456350cb3b9200db24789c.gif\" width=\"200\" />      |\n| Tall grass      | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/769e4a227b430eab1767f80c1da8167eae843053.png\" width=\"200\" />      |\n\n### Revert recipes\n\n| Recipe            | Preview                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |\n| ----------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Clay ball         | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/b75311efb9fefeae4079dfb7ee68f643f5da11be.png\" width=\"200\" />                                                                                                                                       |\n| Glowstone dust    | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/6b55ab09493662a23596615208e0baf026ccb518.png\" width=\"200\" />                                                                                                                                       |\n| Nether wart       | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/3622663f4d31db54138f0d1963b0762a71bb8984.png\" width=\"200\" />                                                                                                                                       |\n| Pointed dripstone | <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DK4Nh8Qe/images/83d0de808439258369f9237bcb4c715a82c35a2b.png\" width=\"200\" /> <br /><img src=\"https://